---
title: Peri Peri Chicken & Feta Wedges with Zesty Baby Broccoli & Aioli
description: We reckon nothing can beat a chicken with a side of wedges and veggies, but this one may be the new best version.
With glowing peri peri sauce for a punch of flavour and a creamy scattering of feta on the wedges, the latest version
sure is new and improved!
